# WooCommerce Integration

## Overview
E-commerce functionality for Arata Vietnam cosmetics distribution with WooCommerce integration.

## Core Files
- **WooCommerce Setup**: [themes/aratavietnam/inc/woocommerce.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/inc/woocommerce.php) - WooCommerce integration
- **Product Templates**: [themes/aratavietnam/single-product.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/single-product.php) - Single product page
- **Product Archive**: [themes/aratavietnam/archive-product.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/archive-product.php) - Product listing
- **Setup Script**: [scripts/setup-woocommerce.sh](mdc:scripts/setup-woocommerce.sh) - WooCommerce configuration

## Product Structure
### Categories
- **8 Main Collections**: Dropdown navigation
- **Subcategories**: Product groupings within collections
- **Featured Products**: Highlighted on homepage

### Product Display
- **Homepage**: 4 featured products (2x2 grid)
- **All Products**: 5 product sets with horizontal scroll
- **Product Pages**: Detailed product information
- **Product Gallery**: Zoom, lightbox, slider support

## Payment Methods
- **COD**: Cash on delivery
- **Bank Transfer**: Direct bank transfer
- **Credit Card**: Online payment via Stripe
- **Reference**: [plugins/woocommerce-gateway-stripe/](mdc:plugins/woocommerce-gateway-stripe/)

## Shipping & Returns
### Shipping Policy
- **Direct Delivery**: Customer pickup at seller location
- **COD Delivery**: Cash on delivery service
- **Online Payment**: Credit card, bank transfer

### Return Policy
- **Time Limit**: 48h notification, 14 days return
- **Conditions**: Wrong items, missing items, damaged packaging
- **Location**: Office/store or postal service

## Customer Management
- **Account System**: Customer registration and login
- **Order History**: Track previous purchases
- **Wishlist**: Save favorite products
- **Reviews**: Product ratings and reviews

## Admin Features
- **Product Management**: Add, edit, categorize products
- **Order Management**: Process orders, update status
- **Inventory**: Stock management
- **Reports**: Sales analytics and reports

## Theme Integration
- **Custom Styling**: Brand-consistent product pages
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-optimized shopping experience
- **Performance**: Optimized for fast loading
- **SEO**: Product page optimization

## Development Commands
```bash
# Setup WooCommerce
docker-compose exec wp-cli wp plugin install woocommerce --activate --allow-root

# Import products
docker-compose exec wp-cli wp import products.xml --authors=create --allow-root

# Configure payment gateway
docker-compose exec wp-cli wp option update woocommerce_stripe_settings --allow-root
```
